<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<wsp:Policy xmlns:L7p="http://www.layer7tech.com/ws/policy" xmlns:wsp="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/ws/2002/12/policy">
    <wsp:All wsp:Usage="Required">
        <L7p:SchemaValidation>
            <L7p:ResourceInfo staticResourceInfo="included">
                <L7p:Document stringValue="<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<s:schema elementFormDefault="qualified"
    targetNamespace="http://warehouse.acme.com/ws"

        <s:complexType>

                <s:element maxOccurs="1" minOccurs="1" name="delay" type="s:int"/>
            </s:sequence>
        </s:complexType>
    </s:element>
    <s:element name="listProductsResponse">
        <s:complexType>
            <s:sequence>
                <s:element maxOccurs="1" minOccurs="0"
                    name="listProductsResult" type="tns:ArrayOfProductListHeader"/>
            </s:sequence>
        </s:complexType>
    </s:element>
    <s:complexType name="ArrayOfProductListHeader">
        <s:sequence>
            <s:element maxOccurs="unbounded" minOccurs="0"
                name="ProductListHeader" nillable="true" type="tns:ProductListHeader"/>
        </s:sequence>
    </s:complexType>
    <s:complexType name="ProductListHeader">
        <s:sequence>
            <s:element maxOccurs="1" minOccurs="0" name="productName" type="s:string"/>
            <s:element maxOccurs="1" minOccurs="1" name="productId" type="s:long"/>
        </s:sequence>
    </s:complexType>
    <s:element name="getProductDetails">
        <s:complexType>
            <s:sequence>
                <s:element maxOccurs="1" minOccurs="1" name="productid" type="s:long"/>
                <s:element maxOccurs="1" minOccurs="1" name="delay" type="s:int"/>
            </s:sequence>
        </s:complexType>
    </s:element>
    <s:element name="getProductDetailsResponse">
        <s:complexType>
            <s:sequence>
                <s:element maxOccurs="1" minOccurs="0"
                    name="getProductDetailsResult" type="tns:ProductDetails"/>
            </s:sequence>
        </s:complexType>
    </s:element>
    <s:complexType name="ProductDetails">
        <s:complexContent mixed="false">
            <s:extension base="tns:ProductListHeader">
                <s:sequence>
                    <s:element maxOccurs="1" minOccurs="0"
                        name="description" type="s:string"/>
                    <s:element maxOccurs="1" minOccurs="1" name="price" type="s:float"/>
                    <s:element maxOccurs="1" minOccurs="1"
                        name="inStock" type="s:boolean"/>
                </s:sequence>
            </s:extension>
        </s:complexContent>
    </s:complexType>
    <s:element name="placeOrder">
        <s:complexType>
            <s:sequence>
                <s:element maxOccurs="1" minOccurs="1" name="productid" type="s:long"/>
                <s:element maxOccurs="1" minOccurs="1" name="amount" type="s:long"/>
                <s:element maxOccurs="1" minOccurs="1" name="price" type="s:float"/>
                <s:element maxOccurs="1" minOccurs="1" name="accountid" type="s:long"/>
                <s:element maxOccurs="1" minOccurs="1" name="delay" type="s:int"/>
            </s:sequence>
        </s:complexType>
    </s:element>
    <s:element name="placeOrderResponse">
        <s:complexType>
            <s:sequence>
                <s:element maxOccurs="1" minOccurs="1"
                    name="placeOrderResult" type="s:long"/>
            </s:sequence>
        </s:complexType>
    </s:element>
    <s:element name="currentOrders">
        <s:complexType>
            <s:sequence>
                <s:element maxOccurs="1" minOccurs="1" name="accountid" type="s:long"/>
                <s:element maxOccurs="1" minOccurs="1" name="delay" type="s:int"/>
            </s:sequence>
        </s:complexType>
    </s:element>
    <s:element name="currentOrdersResponse">
        <s:complexType>
            <s:sequence>
                <s:element maxOccurs="1" minOccurs="0"
                    name="currentOrdersResult" type="tns:ArrayOfOrder"/>
            </s:sequence>
        </s:complexType>
    </s:element>
    <s:complexType name="ArrayOfOrder">
        <s:sequence>
            <s:element maxOccurs="unbounded" minOccurs="0" name="Order"
                nillable="true" type="tns:Order"/>
        </s:sequence>
    </s:complexType>
    <s:complexType name="Order">
        <s:sequence>
            <s:element maxOccurs="1" minOccurs="1" name="date" type="s:dateTime"/>
            <s:element maxOccurs="1" minOccurs="1" name="accountId" type="s:long"/>
            <s:element maxOccurs="1" minOccurs="1" name="productId" type="s:long"/>
            <s:element maxOccurs="1" minOccurs="1" name="amount" type="s:long"/>
            <s:element maxOccurs="1" minOccurs="1" name="price" type="s:float"/>
            <s:element maxOccurs="1" minOccurs="1" name="confirmationId" type="s:long"/>
        </s:sequence>
    </s:complexType>
</s:schema>
"/>
            </L7p:ResourceInfo>
        </L7p:SchemaValidation>
        <L7p:EchoRoutingAssertion/>
    </wsp:All>
</wsp:Policy>
